name: Snap Circuits Jr.
description: Snap Circuits Jr. is a great way to introduce children to electronics. With over 100 projects to work on, this kit teaches kids about circuits, switches, and resistors in a fun and interactive way. The pieces snap together easily, making it simple for young children to build complex circuits.

name: Osmo Genius Starter Kit
description: The Osmo Genius Starter Kit is a great way to teach children language and critical thinking skills. Using the included tablet stand and mirror, children can interact with virtual objects on the screen while learning new words and concepts. The kit includes games that focus on spelling, vocabulary, and problem-solving.

name: Learning Resources Mathlink Cubes
description: The Learning Resources Mathlink Cubes are a great way to teach children math concepts in a hands-on way. These colorful cubes can be snapped together to form patterns, shapes, and even larger objects. With 100 cubes included, there are plenty of possibilities for learning and play.

name: VTech Touch and Learn Activity Desk Deluxe
description: The VTech Touch and Learn Activity Desk Deluxe is a great way to introduce young children to language and reading skills. The desk comes with interactive activity cards that teach letters, numbers, and vocabulary. The desk also includes a music player and phone, so children can have fun while learning.

name: Melissa & Doug Wooden Alphabet Puzzle
description: The Melissa & Doug Wooden Alphabet Puzzle is a fun and educational way for young children to learn the alphabet. The puzzle pieces are brightly colored and easy for small hands to grasp. Each piece also has a picture of an object that starts with the corresponding letter, making it a great way to build vocabulary.

name: Thames & Kosmos Ooze Labs Chemistry Station
description: The Thames & Kosmos Ooze Labs Chemistry Station is a fun and educational way to introduce kids to chemistry. The kit comes with all the materials needed to conduct over 20 experiments, including a beaker, test tubes, and chemicals. Kids will love creating slimy and gooey substances while learning about chemical reactions.

name: Learning Resources Gears! Gears! Gears! Deluxe Building Set
description: The Learning Resources Gears! Gears! Gears! Deluxe Building Set is a great way for kids to learn about engineering and mechanics. The set includes gears, connectors, and cranks that can be snapped together to create complex machines. Kids will love experimenting with different configurations to see what works best.

name: Scientific Explorer My First Mind Blowing Science Kit
description: The Scientific Explorer My First Mind Blowing Science Kit is a great way to introduce kids to basic scientific concepts. The kit includes materials for 11 experiments, such as creating a volcano or making a bouncy ball. Kids will have fun while learning about chemical reactions and the properties of different substances.

name: LeapFrog LeapStart 3D Interactive Learning System
description: The LeapFrog LeapStart 3D Interactive Learning System is a great way to teach kids language and reading skills. The system comes with books that feature interactive activities and games that help develop vocabulary, phonics, and comprehension skills. With its 3D animations and audio feedback, kids will feel like they're playing a video game while learning.

name: Melissa & Doug Solar System 48-Piece Floor Puzzle
description: The Melissa & Doug Solar System 48-Piece Floor Puzzle is a fun and educational way for kids to learn about the solar system. The puzzle pieces are large and easy to handle, making it a great activity for young children. The finished puzzle measures 2 feet by 3 feet, so it's also a great decoration for a child's room.

name: IQ BUILDER 3D Art Coloring Puzzles
description: The IQ BUILDER 3D Art Coloring Puzzles are a great way to teach kids about spatial reasoning and geometry. The set includes 9 different puzzles that can be colored in and assembled into 3D shapes. Kids will have fun while developing their fine motor skills and learning about math concepts.

name: National Geographic Mega Crystal Growing Lab
description: The National Geographic Mega Crystal Growing Lab is a fun and educational way for kids to learn about crystals and geology. The kit includes everything needed to grow 8 different types of crystals, including amethyst and quartz. Kids will love watching as their crystals grow over time.

name: Fat Brain Toys Squigz Deluxe Set
description: The Fat Brain Toys Squigz Deluxe Set is a great way to teach kids about engineering and creativity. The set includes 50 pieces that can be combined in an endless number of ways, allowing kids to create unique structures and designs. The pieces stick together using suction, making it easy for young children to build.

name: Learning Resources Primary Science Lab Activity Set
description: The Learning Resources Primary Science Lab Activity Set is a great way to introduce young children to basic science concepts. The set includes materials for 10 different experiments, such as creating a lava lamp or exploring magnets. The experiments are designed for young children, so they're simple and fun to conduct.

name: VTech KidiZoom Camera Pix
description: The VTech KidiZoom Camera Pix is a great way to teach kids about photography and creativity. The camera features a 2 megapixel sensor and can take both photos and videos. It also includes fun filters and frames that kids can use to customize their pictures. With its durable design, it's perfect for young children to take on adventures.
